p: In District Court of Washington Territory and for the Fourth Judicial District thereof holding terms at Spokane Falls. The Territory of Washington vs. Ray Raymond} Motion Now comes the above named defendant and by her counsel moves the court for a continuance of the above named cause until the next term of the court and bases her said motion on the paper and affidavits here with accompanying and other therein referred to Griffitts Stout & Caton & Stanford Attys for Deft.
